duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide comprehensive mental health assessments and therapeutic interventions for students in schools.
Collaborate with school staff and educational professionals to manage caseload and provide necessary support.
Utilize online assessment and evaluation resources to track student progress and outcomes.
Provide technical support during therapy sessions and ensure a smooth online therapy experience for students.
Participate in clinical mentoring and engage in a supportive online community for professional development.

education_certification.credential: Master's degree in School Psychology or a related field
